{"tid":1164122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[吊命] 美國商務部發臨時許可 放寬華為出口零件禁令","createTime":"2019-05-21T00:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T03:55:27.000Z","uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da1898726d63a3894ca145989d9cc8ec36698ccf","tid":1164122,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:40:21.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/331173/美國發臨時許可-暫時放寬華為出口零件禁令90日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F331173%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF-%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E9%9B%B6%E4%BB%B6%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A490%E6%97%A5&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=930c21fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/331173/美國發臨時許可-暫時放寬華為出口零件禁令90日</a><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部上周四（16日）將華為列入黑名單後引發連鎖反應，據報<strong>Google</strong>等多家企業已暫停向華為提供軟件及貨品；美國商務部周一（20日）發出臨時許可證延遲禁令<span style=\"color: red;\">90天</span>。臨時許可證有效期至<span style=\"color: red;\">2019年8月19日</span>，以便在華為及各方完成相關軟件更新及履行原本合約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic8.dwnews.net/20181224/e2ce200180a514fc51bb6ff322a0d181_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic8.dwnews.net%2F20181224%2Fe2ce200180a514fc51bb6ff322a0d181_w.jpg&h=78bf0227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路透社上周引述商務部指出，有關許可證將不適用於新交易，僅可讓擁有華為設備的公司與個人，有時間維持通訊網路與設備可靠度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/trump-no-huawei-fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2Ftrump-no-huawei-fb.jpg&h=9c47488b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部周四（16日）將華為列入「實體清單」（Entity List），禁止在未獲許可證下與美國企業做生意。實體清單列出的公司，相信涉及違反美國國家安全或外交政策利益活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/krs6jx4YcshfVVU.r7g3Qw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hkej.com/a93268f9a5da60a5bac1c766a40f6603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fkrs6jx4YcshfVVU.r7g3Qw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fhkej.com%2Fa93268f9a5da60a5bac1c766a40f6603&h=30cc9738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨時通用許可證讓華為暫時維持在美國的現有網絡服務，並為當地華為手機用戶提供軟件更新服務，有關臨時許可只適用於<ins>上周四前的合約</ins>。"},{"pid":"8d88e4dee242af38f82c4cbc8380376a9286cd5f","tid":1164122,"uid":58275,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:42:54.000Z","msg":"中國又贏，美帝要跪低了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52c1d8a8eab1849b258986c83218ad98c57e27b","tid":1164122,"uid":171788,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:00.000Z","msg":"美帝真係好撚煩 打就打啦 <br />\n<br />\n仆街 洗唔洗 要唔要我地去美國領使館叫你食屎先"},{"pid":"a82ac548042a6870a0860aa35fbc696709829501","tid":1164122,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f52c1d8a8eab1849b258986c83218ad98c57e27b","tid":1164122,"uid":171788,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:00.000Z","msg":"美帝真係好撚煩 打就打啦 <br />\n<br />\n仆街 洗唔洗 要唔要我地去美國領使館叫你食屎先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:40.000Z","msg":"侵侵係要搵著數，唔係想打死支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4655b9df01a9082c1aea834c1b565de8c4a740","tid":1164122,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82ac548042a6870a0860aa35fbc696709829501","tid":1164122,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f52c1d8a8eab1849b258986c83218ad98c57e27b","tid":1164122,"uid":171788,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:00.000Z","msg":"美帝真係好撚煩 打就打啦 <br />\n<br />\n仆街 洗唔洗 要唔要我地去美國領使館叫你食屎先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:46:40.000Z","msg":"侵侵係要搵著數，唔係想打死支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-2